1999.HK&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=95da2fda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01999.HK</a>)  +0.300 (+4.478%)    沽空 $7.63千萬; 比率 28.702%   。他於公布前對傳媒表示，已對相關企業作出詳細研究，相信當中存在瞞騙(fraud)，實際盈利情況亦不如其披露數字。<br />\n<br />\n他於較早前表示，公布是次沽空目標後，一段時間不會再狙擊港股。(vi/da)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2017-06-07 12:25。)<br />\n<br />\nSource: aastock"},{"pid":"451b14712aee3cd9525ef7feb3e0235bcae8b750","tid":274144,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"其實1999 都好熱門，對比番都係沽空大增"},{"pid":"9a19f3fd4dfdcffc4e4ec962e266bdaa1e19b175","tid":274144,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:22:24.000Z","msg":"變左估會唔會停牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e092044e53de14447cbd612c2d6d2de86ad611f","tid":274144,"uid":93662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"里昂表示，將敏華(<a href=\"http://01999.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01999.HK&d=RqhwnB06MJQCJkBLgkiVqp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=95da2fda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01999.HK</a>)  +0.300 (+4.478%)    沽空 $7.63千萬; 比率 28.702%   目標價由7.1元升至8.3元，維持「買入」評級。<br />\n<br />\n里昂表示，敏華去年純利按年升32%至17.5億元，高於該行預測7.2%，以及市場預測7.9%，再次證明其增長穩定。該行預期敏華增長前景穩定，主要因為北美銷售可能復甦、中國銷售仍強勁、Home Group擴展及毛利率穩定，帶動2017-2020息稅前盈利複合增長達17%，從而帶動股價進一步上揚。公司現金流仍強勁，亦支持未來回購股份、派息及潛在併購。(ad/u)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2017-06-07 12:25。)"},{"pid":"0dbf0d88528e7aacb0d419694b4d23e6105d4535","tid":274144,"uid":47776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變左估會唔會停牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n估唔到佢唔係直插無水花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢反而依定護盤護得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b701e6e5e40246c515c25fe4182e2f3399